                            oc:contentOrder 1 ;
                            oc:textContent "After the blind comparator determines a winner, the Post-hoc Analyzer \"unblids\" the results by examining the skills and transcripts. The goal is to extract actionable insights: what made the winner better, and how can the loser be improved?" ] ;
